R-scape v2.6.4.b November 2025
	Fixes issue with aggregated E-values. The case of "no aggregated evalue calculated" was not considered properly.

R-scape v2.6.4.c December 2025
	updated config.guess/config.sub files to automake-1.18
	configure.ac modified so that if bison is not install, tornado does not get configured.

R-scape v2.6.4.d December 2025
	configure.ac modified so that if bison is not install, tornado does not get configured.
	
R-scape v2.6.6 May 2026
	updated script pdb_parse.pl and library PDBFUNCS.pm to deal with pdb files that only include the ATOMS fields

R-scape v2.6.7 May 2026
	It compiles correctly if bison is not installed. Then, tornado is not compiled.

R-scape v2.6.8 June 2026
	Fixed some warning/error in RNAVIEW that made the compilation fail in some systems

R-scape v2.6.9 June 2026
	RBG CYK allows internal looks larger than MAXLOOP_I. Otherwise, cyk may return -infty due to other constraints
	The xxx.cacofold.sto original alignment annotated with the CaCoFold structure now reports the extra structural annotations adding their nane: SS_cons_pk1, SS_cons_tr1,...
	The R2R.sto alignments (used only for R2R plotting) are not produced by default. Need to use option --r2rmsa to produce them.
	Files .cov and .power have two columns added describing: the number of sequences that contain the pair, and the % of those that are canonical base pairs (AU,UA,CG,GC,GU,UG).

R-scape v2.6.9.a June 2026
	Fix a type in the configure.ac file that described the version as v2.6.0 instead of v2.6.9

R-scape v2.6.10 July 2026
	Documantation updated with new formats for .cov and .power files
	Need to rethink the cyk algorithm regarding MAXLOOP_I, previous fix was taking too long.
